snippet.title: EA Sports FC 24 - Official UEFA Euro 2024 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
EA Sports FC 24 is welcoming the most prestigious championship in Europe UEFA Euro 2024 to the game as a free in-game update. Players who play EA Sports FC 24 by January 16, 2024 will be able to gain access to one of Europe’s biggest stars as an exclusive, untradeable Ultimate Team Player item such as Jack Grealish or Federico Chiesa. UEFA Euro 2024 arrives to EA Sports FC 24 in Summer 2024 for PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, and Nintendo Switch.

#EASportsFC24 #UEFAEuro2024
